column5: Hello Going to Frog Rapids camp the first of July. I was wondering if I could get information on the camp and fishing Sturgeon River,Botsford Lake, Abram Chute and Minnitaki Lake.Thank you for any information, Have a Great Day
i didn,t think anyone went there anymore. my best friend burnt to death there 50 years ago. never been there since.
Frog Rapids Camp is a very nice, well kept camp that has a location that is very accessible. I'm sure they will treat you well. Have no fear.
